<HEAD>Union Official Killed in Truck Bomb Explosion</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MERRILLVILLE, Ind. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A powerful bomb exploded while a
construction union official was starting his truck Wednesday,
killing the man and hurling his body about 50 feet, police said.
   Joseph Bova, 43, was financial secretary and a part-time field
representative for Laborers Local 81 in Valparaiso. His truck had
